Step 1: Create Matrix for Drill Through Cont. Part 4

- Change the field for Homework Link to .Homework Link (this is a measure) then you will need to rename and format the size of your columns so that they all fit within the matrix.




- Select Conditional Formatting and then choose HW Link, you will turn on Web URL and then select advanced controls. You will format based on screenshot below. You want to make sure that based field to Homework Link column (not the measure).
